# Solution

Context()->texStrings;
SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$PAR Solution: $PAR
\( S \cup T \) is not a sentence.  \( x \geq $c \) is not a set: \( \lbrace x \geq $c \rbrace \) is.  You can not join together two inequalities pointing different directions. $BR
END_SOLUTION
